HTML Theming
You can do extensive additional customization using SASS theme files.

Bootstrap defines over 1,400 variables that control fonts, colors, padding, borders, and much more!

```{css}
/*-- scss:defaults --*/

$body-bg: #CDEEFD;

/*-- scss:rules --*/
h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
  text-shadow: -1px -1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .3);
}
```
